<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
      <h1 style="color: #DC2626;">새로운 예약이 접수되었습니다</h1>
      
      <p>새로운 AI 코칭 예약이 접수되었습니다.</p>
      
      <div style="background-color: #FEF2F2; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #DC2626;">
        <h2 style="color: #1F2937; margin-top: 0;">예약 정보</h2>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
          <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>이름:</strong> <%= @reservation.name %></li>
          <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>연락처:</strong> <%= @reservation.phone %></li>
          <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>이메일:</strong> <%= @reservation.email %></li>
          <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>예약 일시:</strong> <%= @reservation.reservation_datetime.strftime("%Y년 %m월 %d일 %H시 %M분") %></li>
          <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>코칭 형태:</strong> <%= @reservation.coaching_type %></li>
          <% if @reservation.selected_subjects.any? %>
            <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>선택 과목:</strong> <%= @reservation.selected_subjects.join(", ") %></li>
          <% end %>
          <% if @reservation.requests.present? %>
            <li style="margin: 10px 0;"><strong>요청사항:</strong> <%= @reservation.requests %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p style="color: #6B7280; font-size: 12px;">
        예약 ID: #<%= @reservation.id %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

